git init
ls -a : show hidden files too
Staging are status : git status in cmd
git status :: red ones  are not in staging are (are not being followed by git), green ones are being following by git.
git add chapter1.txt :: add chapter 1 to staging area
git commit - m "Name of change" :: use present word better - complete chapter1
git add . :: add all files to staging area
git log :: see all commits , "head" shows the current position
git diff file.txt:: will show differences
git checkout file.txt :: will reward all last changes we had for chapter 3
